window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Was the biggest case of his career the worst mistake he ever made?</p> <p>Ten years ago, DCI Jack Logan stopped the serial child-killer dubbed \"Mister Whisper\", earning himself a commendation, a drinking problem, and a broken marriage in the process.</p> <p>Now, he spends his days working in Glasgow's Major Investigations Team, and his nights reliving the horrors of what he saw.</p> <p>And what he did.</p> <p>When another child disappears a hundred miles north in the Highlands, Jack is sent to lead the investigation and bring the boy home.</p> <p>But as similarities between the two cases grow, could it be that Jack caught the wrong man all those years ago?</p> <p>And, if so, is the real Mister Whisper about to claim his fourth victim?</p> <p><i>A Litter of Bones</i> is the explosive debut crime thriller novel from JD Kirk, an exciting new voice in Scottish crime fiction.</p>"; 
